        "text": "<p>Most cleansers leave skin feeling tight.</p><p>That feeling isn’t clean - it’s moisture loss.</p><p>Many cleansers rely on strong surfactants to create a foamy, squeaky clean feel, often at the expense of your skin barrier.</p><p>Our cleanser is different. Instead of relying on water alone, the formula is powered by 50% glycerin, a moisture loving ingredient that helps skin hold onto hydration while you cleanse.</p>",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/cleanser-bg-image-1.webp",
        "image_mobile": "shopify://shop_images/cleanser-bg-image-1-mob.webp",
        "button_label": "",
        "button_url": ""
      }
    },
